## ğŸ”Œ Pluggable Architecture

Switch backends by changing environment variables - **zero code changes!**

```bash
# Event Bus
EVENT_BUS_TYPE=redis_stream + REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379     # Current âœ…
EVENT_BUS_TYPE=kafka + KAFKA_SERVERS=localhost:9092                 # Coming soon ğŸš§
EVENT_BUS_TYPE=rabbitmq + RABBITMQ_URL=amqp://localhost             # Coming soon ğŸš§

# Storage
STORAGE_BACKEND=redis + REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379            # Production âœ…
STORAGE_BACKEND=json + JSON_STORAGE_DIR=./data                      # Development âœ…
STORAGE_BACKEND=postgresql + POSTGRES_URL=postgresql://...          # Coming soon ğŸš§
STORAGE_BACKEND=mongodb + MONGODB_URI=mongodb://...                 # Coming soon ğŸš§
```

